       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ACCT-BALANCE.
      * ACCOUNT BALANCE CHECKER - SIMPLE LOW RISK MODULE

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT ACCOUNT-FILE ASSIGN TO "ACCT.DAT"
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD ACCOUNT-FILE.
       01 ACCOUNT-RECORD.
           05 ACCT-NUMBER  PIC 9(10).
           05 ACCT-BALANCE PIC 9(8)V99 COMP-3.
           05 ACCT-TYPE    PIC X(5).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-TOTAL-BALANCE PIC 9(12)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-EOF           PIC X VALUE 'N'.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           OPEN INPUT ACCOUNT-FILE
           READ ACCOUNT-FILE AT END MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF
           PERFORM SUM-BALANCES UNTIL WS-EOF = 'Y'
           CLOSE ACCOUNT-FILE
           STOP RUN.

       SUM-BALANCES.
           ADD ACCT-BALANCE TO WS-TOTAL-BALANCE
           READ ACCOUNT-FILE AT END MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF.
